{"article_id":"dIN6zQZmahp77mIw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Reade ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"who has alleged","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Joe Biden assaulted her in 1993 ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"believes","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"the media is applying a double standard to her story","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"and Democrats aren ' t taking her seriously .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"Max Whittaker / The New York Times","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"via Redux","depth":3},{"id":8,"text":"Tara Reade , a former aide to Joe Biden , April 11 .","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"She has seen Joe Biden take questions on cable news and late-night television .","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"She has seen him host virtual town halls with voters and online fundraisers with donors .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"And from her home in California ,","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"where she is keeping a daily watch on Twitter ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"Tara Reade has been waiting for someone","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"- anyone -","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"to ask the former vice president about her story .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"\" He was on television twice today .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"No one asked him .","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"No one ' s asking the question , \"","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"Reade said in a phone interview earlier this month .","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"\" No one ' s even posing the question. \"","depth":14},{"id":21,"text":"On that particular day , Biden sat for an interview with Joe Scarborough and Mika Brzezinski on MSNBC ' s Morning Joe ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"appeared on a CNN coronavirus town hall with Anderson Cooper ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"and took questions during a 45-minute fundraiser with dozens of donors .","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"More than a month after Reade first detailed a serious allegation of sexual assault ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Biden is set to address the subject in a Morning Joe interview","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"scheduled for Friday morning .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"For weeks , he didn ' t receive a question about the claims ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"despite doing multiple interviews .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Reade ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"who has fielded dozens of requests from reporters this month ,","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"she is acutely aware","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"that her allegations pose complex terrain for the \" mainstream media ' s \" coverage of a Democratic Party","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"that has long viewed both Biden as a beloved figure and President Donald Trump as a man","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"accused of sexism and more than a dozen instances of sexual harassment and assault .","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"As Democrats came to Biden ' s defense this month as an advocate for women","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"- marking a turn for a party","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"that has embraced the notion of \" believing women \" as a baseline posture in the # MeToo era -","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Reade said","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"she believes","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"her story has been given short shrift","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"compared to other accusations of sexual abuse against powerful figures .","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"She named as an example Christine Blasey Ford , the woman","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"who said","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"she was sexually assaulted by Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh , then Trump ' s nominee to the court .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"After seeing her story refracted through the lens of Political Twitter ,","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"Reade said in a series of interviews this month","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"she ' s felt \" marginalized , \" \" smeared , \" and \" discounted \" - betrayed by Democrats","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"she said","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"she once admired .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"\" It was really devastating","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"when [ Kirsten ] Gillibrand and Stacey Abrams and Hillary Clinton , all on the same day , just basically implied","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"my story was n't true","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"and they believe Joe Biden .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"I can ' t describe to you","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"what that felt like , \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Reade said on Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"describing herself as a \" lifelong Democrat \" and in particular a fan of Abrams ' , the former Georgia House minority leader","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"who has been campaigning","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"to serve on the ticket with Biden as his vice presidential nominee .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"\" I just- I ' m stunned , \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Reade said .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"\" They did n't just say ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"' Oh , we 're standing with Joe Biden","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"until we hear more. '","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"They just discounted me .","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"They marginalized me .","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"They said","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"they did n't believe me .","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"I ca n't tell you , \"","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"Reade said ,","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"trailing off .","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"\" I cried for a while","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"because they 're important in my life .","depth":14},{"id":75,"text":"They 've been figures","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"that I looked up to . \"","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"At points over the last month , Reade has been scrutinized as much as her allegations .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Some Democrats have pointed to her pro-Bernie Sanders tweets","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"( \" Bernie stay in ! \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"she tweeted in late March ) ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"her writings","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"praising Vladimir Putin","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"( she told earlier this month","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"that she had changed her views about Putin","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"after reading writers like Julia Ioffe and Russian opposition activist Alexei Navalny ) ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"and her decision","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"to first seek a platform for her story on left-wing media outlets like Katie Halper ' s podcast","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"( \" She 's very trauma-informed , \"","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"she says of Halper )","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"as markers of her credibility .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Reade , a 56-year-old","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"who says","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"she put herself through law school as a single mother","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"and still has hundreds of thousands of dollars in student and medical debt ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"says","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"she is not ashamed to identify herself as \" a working-class poor person. \"","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"She has followed the online discussion , political and academic , over the ways","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"in which survivors are received in the public square .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"\" I am not an ' imperfect victim , ' \"","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Reade tweeted on Tuesday .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"Reade has accused Biden of digitally penetrating her in a Senate hallway","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"when she was a staff assistant in his Senate office in 1993 .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"She has said","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"she filed a Senate personnel report at the time ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"told others in the office about the incident ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"and was removed from her duty","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"of overseeing the interns .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"The Biden campaign has said","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"the incident did not happen .","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"Three former Senate aides ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"all of whom","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Reade said","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"she complained to directly at the time about the assault ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"have said","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"they don ' t remember any such complaint","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"or that it did not take place .","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"One of them , Biden ' s former executive assistant from 1982 to 2000 , Marianne Baker , said in a statement","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"provided by the campaign","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that she never once witnessed or heard of \" any reports of inappropriate conduct , period - not from Ms. Reade , not from anyone. \"","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Subsequent reporting has corroborated elements of Reade ' s story .","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"Former interns from the Senate office remember Reade being reassigned away from managing them ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"according to the New York Times .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"After Reade mentioned","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"that her mother had called into Larry King Live ,","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"the Intercept published the transcript from a 1993 episode","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"where a caller described her daughter ' s negative experience with a \" prominent senator , \"","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"though the caller does not detail the nature of the experience .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"Across different outlets , people","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"who knew Reade","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"have said","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"she told them","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"that she had had a bad experience with her boss in Washington","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"- with varied levels of detail .","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"In an interview with Business Insider , a former neighbor , Lynda LaCasse , said","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Reade detailed her full allegation against Biden in the 1990s .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"The New York Times and Washington Post each reported","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"they spoke with an unnamed friend","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"who had said","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Reade told her about the allegation in the 1990s as well .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"Others have provided more limited accounts","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"- one friend told the Washington Post , for instance ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"that she remembered Reade saying","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"Biden touched her arm","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"and behaved inappropriately ,","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"but did not have other details .","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"Reade ' s brother initially told the Post","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"he remembered her telling him","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"that Biden was \" inappropriate , \"","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"but followed up days later","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"to clarify","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"that he recalled Reade telling him","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"that the then-senator had put his hands under her clothes .","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"Through it all , Biden himself has remained silent .","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"Publicly , aides have referred reporters back to a single statement ,","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"dated April 13 ,","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"while the former vice president believes","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"women should have the space","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"to tell their stories ,","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"this incident didn ' t occur .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"Privately , they have distributed talking points to other Democrats","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"advising them to rely on a New York Times investigation","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"and to","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"( inaccurately )","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"insist","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"the article concluded","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"the incident never happened .","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"Though the mainstream media has now started to aggressively cover the story ,","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"Reade has been disappointed with the length of time","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"it took major news outlets","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"to cover her allegation , as well as the tone of some of the coverage .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"Last year","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"- when other women had come forward","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"to say","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"Biden had touched them in a way","depth":15},{"id":177,"text":"that made them uncomfortable -","depth":15},{"id":178,"text":"Reade told her local paper","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"while working for the former senator ,","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"he touched her neck and shoulders .","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"In the same 2019 column , she said","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"a supervisor told her","depth":12},{"id":184,"text":"that Biden wanted her to serve drinks at an event","depth":13},{"id":185,"text":"because he liked the way","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"she looked .","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"When she refused ,","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"Reade told the newspaper ,","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"her responsibilities were reduced .","depth":11},{"id":190,"text":"This spring , she turned to leftist outlets","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"to tell her serious allegation of sexual assault by Biden ,","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"appearing on Halper ' s podcast and Democracy Now .","depth":8},{"id":193,"text":"\" I used to think","depth":9},{"id":194,"text":"that a Republican talking point was to call the mainstream media biased , \"","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"Reade said .","depth":8},{"id":196,"text":"\" So I used to think ,","depth":10},{"id":197,"text":"Oh , that 's just a talking point for them .","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"I do n't believe it .","depth":9},{"id":199,"text":"But now I 'm living it [ in ] real time ,","depth":11},{"id":200,"text":"and I see it -","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"like , I see it for what it is .","depth":12},{"id":202,"text":"Because I am a Democrat ,","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"or I was .","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"But now I 'm not anything , really .","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"I ' m politically homeless . \"","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":411,"left":211,"right":410,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":209,"right":210,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left":208,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":0,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":207,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":410,"left":212,"right":409,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":212,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":409,"left":304,"right":408,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":304,"left":8,"right":303,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":303,"left":248,"right":302,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":231,"right":247,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":226,"right":230,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":226,"left":213,"right":225,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":213,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":225,"left":217,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":214,"right":216,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":214,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration"